## Output Formatting

- Use plain text only — no ANSI escape codes, no Unicode box-drawing
- Use `==` headers for sections: `== Section Name ==`
- Use stat lines with aligned colons for key-value data
- Use Markdown tables (`| Col | Col |`) for tabular data
- Format large numbers with comma separators (e.g., `3,847`)
- Format percentages with one decimal and raw counts: `95.9% (3,691/3,847)`
- Output must be copy-pasteable into GitHub issues, Slack, and docs

